These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, december, march
1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
2. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Birthday   | march | july | september | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, asparagus, artichoke, avocado
1. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person eating avocado##5
2. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
3. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Food   | peach | avocado | asparagus | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, zinnia, amaryllis, daisy
1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaisy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Flower   | daisy | daffodil | amaryllis | zinnia |

