.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
House: cottage, modern, wooden, townhouse
1. the wooden house is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
3. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| House   | townhouse | modern | wooden | cottage |

