.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
City: nizza, miami, berlin, paris
1. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to berlin##2
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| City   | berlin | miami | paris | nizza |

