.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, satire, comedy, zombie
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
2. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie | satire | comedy |

