1. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
2. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Game   | backgammon | monopoly | canasta | poker |

